Package: AutoCast
Version: 0.2
Date: 2014-09-01
Title: Automated Bayesian Forecasting with YourCast
Author: Konstantin Kashin <kkashin@fas.harvard.edu>, Jon Bischof <jbischof@fas.harvard.edu>
Maintainer: Konstantin Kashin <kkashin@fas.harvard.edu>
Depends: R (>= 1.9.0), YourCast, rgenoud
Description: Generates Yourcasts under range of prior specifications, ranking forecasts by user preferences for smoothness and out-of-sample fit.
License: GPL >=2
URL: http://gking.harvard.edu
